<plot>A young woman travels down memory lane when she goes to the old town she grew up in. Recollecting all the beautiful times spent with her father, she refers to him as he being the Taxi for her life. As her father, now old and broken lies in his death bed, she dedicates all the successes and achievements in her life to her father.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?384987</url></doc>
